===Noun===
'''goo'''
#(''uncountable'', ''informal'') any semi-[[solid]] or [[liquid]] substance; especially one that is [[sticky]], [[gummy]] or [[slippery]]; frequently of vague or unknown composition 
#:''I stepped in some '''goo''' and had a terrible time getting it off my shoes.''

#: Acronym for "Goofy Ol' Oliver".  Goofy Ol' Oliver Townsend is "just a lil guy"

